name: 10-25976-ubs3-6743
notes: This data set includes water quality data collected by Ottawa Riverkeeper's Riverwatch network during the Spring, Summer and Fall of 2013 to 2023. The water quality characteristics mainly include water and air temperature, pH, and Secchi Depth. Some sites also include measurements of conductivity, dissolved oxygen, nitrate, nitrite, alkalinity and hardness. Sites are located throughout the Ottawa River watershed, mainly along the mainstem of the river.

notes_translated.en: This data set includes water quality data collected by Ottawa Riverkeeper's Riverwatch network during the Spring, Summer and Fall of 2013 to 2023. The water quality characteristics mainly include water and air temperature, pH, and Secchi Depth. Some sites also include measurements of conductivity, dissolved oxygen, nitrate, nitrite, alkalinity and hardness. Sites are located throughout the Ottawa River watershed, mainly along the mainstem of the river.
notes_translated.fr: Cet ensemble de données comprend des données sur la qualité de l'eau recueillies par le réseau Riverwatch des Gardiens de la rivière des Outaouais au cours du printemps, de l'été et de l'automne 2013 à 2023. Les caractéristiques de qualité de l'eau comprennent principalement la température de l'eau et de l'air, le pH et la profondeur de Secchi. Certains sites incluent également des mesures de conductivité, d'oxygène dissous, de nitrate, de nitrite, d'alcalinité et de dureté. Les sites sont situés dans tout le bassin versant de la rivière des Outaouais, principalement le long du cours principal de la rivière.
